1236
01:28:14,070 --> 01:28:24,614
Be it further resolved by the Memphis City Council that we invite the mayor of Memphis and the Memphis School Committee to submit a joint resolution declaring systemic racism as a public health emergency.

1237
01:28:25,435 --> 01:28:26,095
